long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Influenced by the likes of Banksy, Shepard Fairey, and Obey Giant, this extension transforms your browser background into a dynamic canvas with each search. Uncover hidden gems and renowned murals from cities around the globe, all in one seamless experience. Our extension also provides an enhanced search experience as well as shortcuts for quick access to your favorite sites.

Get ready to embark on an art-filled adventure with every new tab. Download Street Art Tab now and let the streets become your canvas! 

By clicking "Add to chrome", I accept and agree to installing Street Art Tab extension which will have a search feature provided by Microsoft Bing and be governed by our service, Terms of Use at https://street-art.digitreesolutions.com.au/terms and Privacy Policy at https://street-art.digitreesolutions.com.au/privacy.
